nnoremap <Leader>bj <Plug>BookmarkMoveDown| " 书签: 当前书签行下移
nnoremap <Leader>bl <Plug>BookmarkMoveToLine| " 书签: 书签移动到某一行


" vim-bookmarks 书签插件配置 }

